    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/36e2ff3973ed51b5fd3f491625ecd437.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><strong>MangaKa</strong>  是一个可以帮助在作品中使用线条艺术的艺术家，无论是作为参考、指南，还是作为最终渲染，帮助他们节省制作时间并加快工作流程的工具！<br><br>（所有渲染图像均可用于商业目的，例如漫画、插图、故事板等。）<br><br>您可以在此处找到完整的内容列表：<br><br><br>基础软件包括以下库：<br><br>- 透视块<br>- 基本人体模型套装<br>- 基本形状模型<br>- 室内平面图模型<br>- 基本墙壁、窗户和门<br>- 简单的家具<br>- 简单的室内道具<br>- 基本建筑物。<br>- 家用电器。<br>- 道路。<br>- 街头道具。<br>- 汽车。<br>- 树木和石头。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >透视工具</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/a135f1252bfb14a1b079ee997d6b85c0.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=384 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 带有线条切换的透视块。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在“透视”和稳定模式之间切换。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 网格和水平线。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D人体模型</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/3706ef1d378b687f2e6507b624a2ca21.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/0096cdee1e9ce6d56fbf8c1ddf3f400b.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/30d4f0d204eb9b034b88360bcb55d6bc.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/a8e633712d550f19249a3b2c60505630.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/c5370663f4eaedf8a01f22367e62c24d.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 使用拖动节点轻松摆出角色姿势。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 根据您的需要更改面部指南。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 更改面部纹理，或添加自己的纹理。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 姿势和手势库。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 多变的体型。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 切换身体部位的可见性</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 将任何 3D 对象附加到主体上。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 保存/加载人体模型配置文件</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D 库 (DLC)</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/4dc50007238b36fcde8d8eb62c271d84.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=340 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/787c769c710ab8fb0089cd6a2c8b0054.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/eced6912ff0d4103fa6f75f200e36fe4.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 各种主题和时代的库。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 材料和零件上的可定制对象。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 模块化和非模块化对象。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 具有自动生成功能的选定对象（即书架上的书籍和装饰品）。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >相机滤镜</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 各种相机滤镜，有助于获得替代效果</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D 工具包 (DLC)</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/d38620d2776e39221829eaa53ba313bc.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2D 对象库，有助于改善视觉效果。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在 3D 空间中导入您自己的图像。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在 2D 面板中导入您自己的图像作为参考。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 内置互联网浏览器。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >导入您自己的 3D 模型 (DLC)</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/5a76da4c9366c8a491719291999421af.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 导入您自己的 3D 模型。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 支持动画模型。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 支持的3D格式：FBX，OBJ，GLTF2，STL，PLY，3MF</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >渲染</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/7aca3eb2645b0cd6f7a9ca068a43838f.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/050e19655e6b7731018316b94807eda4.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234500/extras/afeab0acd93ede3d0cabecec801fce6a.avif?t=1717078366\" width=512 height=352 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 将图像渲染为 PNG。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 支持透明背景。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 支持渲染区域。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 渲染高达屏幕尺寸的 5 倍。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他功能</h2>除了上述主要功能之外，<strong>MangaKa</strong>还提供了以下工具和功能，使您的工作更轻松：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 各种转换工具和复制方法。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 对齐网格或对象函数。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在变换工具的“本地”和“全局”方向之间切换。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可调自由度（视深）</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可调整线条属性、轮廓颜色和可见性切换。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 各种图案和阴影材料。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 能够导入自己的纹理。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可更改的背景纹理（纸张）。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 宁静的背景音乐，帮助您放松！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 全屏模式。</li></ul>",
